C     IPMPAR IS AN ADAPTATION OF THE FUNCTION I1MACH, WRITTEN BY
C     P.A. FOX, A.D. HALL, AND N.L. SCHRYER (BELL LABORATORIES).
C     IPMPAR WAS FORMED BY A.H. MORRIS (NSWC). THE CONSTANTS ARE
